{"tid":1468954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一click,癱瘓政府網站","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:42:56.000Z","uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb1d289de1557176ad8f7bbdeecb2435c231ced","tid":1468954,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:33:10.000Z","msg":"搞公投雖然可以反映民意，但係現今呢個情況基本上冇可能<br />\n<br />\n之前見到新界北警署係元朗襲擊過晚三個鐘頭24,000個電話，令我諗到其實用DDOS癱瘓政府網站絕對有可能<br />\n<br />\n我唔係指一嘅DDOS攻擊，就算有IT人高超到可以單人匹馬搞掂，我都唔建議任何神人去冒險俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我講緊嘅係一人一票普選咁款click落條link度</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">全部唔滿意政府嘅今日1:00食飯嘅時候一齊咁耐政府新聞網度, 等佢唔好再廢噏</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n切記真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好用軟件</span>以身犯法，我哋要一人一下咁話俾政府聽，反送中嘅市民數量已經多到可以隊冧你個政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Findex.html&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fbfc9e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"64eb8c2533e6d591606e20c1172d2f45a4619d52","tid":1468954,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:33:50.000Z","msg":"記得今日1:00!!!"},{"pid":"9e464c5cc97186b12668a780962db1046ed1e8f5","tid":1468954,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}